original_title: Thong Girl 3: Revenge of the Dark Widow
overview: Thong Girl returns in yet another high-flying adventure, but this time it's a double-trouble for our superhoeros and the stakes are high. Thong Girl and her trusty sidekick Boxer Brief Boy take on the combined forces of the evil Chaz Chernobyl and The Dark Widow.
title: Thong Girl 3: Revenge of the Dark Widow
